title: Jenner shows off a new shaggy wet-look 'do
text:
She's not one to rest on her laurels when it comes to hairstyles.
And Kylie Jenner, 19, displayed her latest look at the Alexander Wang Fall/Winter 2017 runway collection on Saturday, showing off a striking shaggy style.
The 19-year-old reality star attended to support sister Kendall who was walking in the show, and she flaunted her ample bosom and taut tummy in a strapless black cropped top with cutout panels throughout the midsection.
Scroll down for video
Proud: Kylie Jenner, 19, attended the Alexander Wang Fall/Winter 2017 runway show as she showed support for sister Kendall Jenner, 21, who walked in the highly-coveted show
The Keeping Up With The Kardashians was joined by her rapper boyfriend Tyga, 27, as the pair made a showstopping arrival.
Kylie teamed the revealing low-cut number with matching skintight leggings that encased her lean limbs.
She layered a red and black plaid coat over her eye-catching ensemble and added a pair of studded stilettos for an edgy touch.
Revealing: The 19-year-old flaunted her ample bosom and taut tummy in a strapless black cropped top with cutout panels throughout the midsection
Perfect pair: The Keeping Up With The Kardashians was joined by her rapper boyfriend Tyga, 27, as the pair made a showstopping arrival
Her raven tresses showed off a wet look hairdo and hit just to her shoulders. She also skipped the accessories, allowing her attire to take center stage.
Tyga made sure to stand out from the crowd in a bright yellow leather jacket with fuzzy trim.
He wore all black beneath and dark movie star shades while showing off several diamond chains and stud earrings.
Lean limbs: Kylie teamed the revealing low-cut number with matching skintight leggings that encased her slender legs
Check-er out! The reality star layered a red and black plaid coat over her eye-catching ensemble
Fancy footwear! Kylie added a pair of black leather studded stilettos for an edgy touch
The younger sister of Kim Kardashian took to Snapchat and posted several videos with her supermodel sister Kendall, 21.
The Victoria's Secret model donned an all black ensemble in figure-hugging black leather high-waisted pants.
Also walking in Wang's show was Bella Hadid, 20, who wore a pair of black opaque tights and leather shorts.
She teamed the look with a black and white printed long-sleeved top while making her way down the catwalk.
